{"tid":2012213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱為改善空氣 深圳禁露天燒烤","createTime":"2020-05-11T13:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T14:34:27.000Z","uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"454718fc436672f1a8d3d338550b99f1ddf05e8e","tid":2012213,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:24:09.000Z","msg":"稱為改善空氣 深圳禁露天燒烤<br />\n更新時間 (HKT):02:20 0511<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200511/large/1589127508_8b5d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200511%2Flarge%2F1589127508_8b5d.gif&h=9ef9461f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣州9月至11月禁止露天燒烤。<br />\n<br />\n內地就連BBQ都有罪，與香港只有一線之隔的深圳市將出台新規，禁止所有露天燒烤，官方解釋希望藉此改善空氣質素，守護「深圳藍」。內地至今已有多個城市出台相同規定；但有不少網民反問「燒烤能有多少污染？跟工業污染比差遠了吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民：工業污染更嚴重<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於往年內地頻發霧霾天氣事件，深圳市大氣污染防治指揮部近日印發《2020年「深圳藍」可持續行動計劃》，明確提出「將露天燒烤納入環境監管網格化管理，依法查處露天燒烤行為，全面禁止露天燒烤。」禁止露天燒烤是許多省遇到嚴重污染天氣時的應急措施之一，如2017年陝西西安、2018年山西太原，及2019年海南海口市等，都有類似政策，也有一些城市劃出「經營區域」准許露天燒烤，其他一律禁止，但今次深圳卻是「一刀切」全禁。<br />\n<br />\n有深圳市民向媒體說：「露天燒烤確實有損城市形象，油煙味確實會損害大家利益，損害城市整體美觀。有那種去油煙的燒烤，在室內還是可以的。」<br />\n<br />\n也有人稱「我覺得要分地方，像海邊密度比較低，影響不了周圍人，對別人侵擾比較少的情況下，還是可以適度放開。」也有網民質疑「燒烤能有多少污染？跟工業污染比，差遠了吧」！<br />\n澎湃新聞網"},{"pid":"da6712fe8e8745489c494a03c30f69e2cde439eb","tid":2012213,"uid":135277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"轉室內燒"},{"pid":"81a4c3bc894336ed4dcca2c5131426122f0f2fce","tid":2012213,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:27:18.000Z","msg":"永遠唔知自己錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過得政黎<br />\n禁柒哂去最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9511cecdd2b86af11896999fe96b81bd55e0e3d7","tid":2012213,"uid":72185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:27:55.000Z","msg":"咁人地焚化爐要燒人嘛<br />\n係要係其他地方減少污染"},{"pid":"e0603f7d524eb13d4cdfe53a8c654e4e8ccbb7f9","tid":2012213,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:28:01.000Z","msg":"燒烤違法，又可以罰錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近深圳政府好窮，係咁抄牌<br />\n汽車、電動車都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d362a5a75fa9a5b9c2417147e698bbcc126b46","tid":2012213,"uid":76591,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"81a4c3bc894336ed4dcca2c5131426122f0f2fce","tid":2012213,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:27:18.000Z","msg":"永遠唔知自己錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過得政黎<br />\n禁柒哂去最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:28:36.000Z","msg":"想罰錢咋，最近深圳政府窮<br />\n你以為真係為空氣好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0676f128f8238f0e1e07e7f89b65769f5d3ecf67","tid":2012213,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:28:42.000Z","msg":"老鼠肉"},{"pid":"2ba0c5d51a2ed13bbedae66d5f6e0850faea4034","tid":2012213,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:29:19.000Z","msg":"個個都做小販邊個租鋪賣地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f1ed771e8a508fcdf534c1bc8327404f8c593d","tid":2012213,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81a4c3bc894336ed4dcca2c5131426122f0f2fce","tid":2012213,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:27:18.000Z","msg":"永遠唔知自己錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過得政黎<br />\n禁柒哂去最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:29:24.000Z","msg":"得定德"},{"pid":"7539fdaf765431702015457031d0f0b6372ee48b","tid":2012213,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco